PEI_APRIORI_FILE_CONTENTS Struct Reference


Data Fields

EFI_GUID FileNamesWithinVolume [1]

Detailed Description

This file must be of type EFI_FV_FILETYPE_FREEFORM and must contain a single section of type EFI_SECTION_RAW. For details on firmware volumes, firmware file types, and firmware file section types.

Field Documentation

EFI_GUID PEI_APRIORI_FILE_CONTENTS::FileNamesWithinVolume[1]

An array of zero or more EFI_GUID type entries that match the file names of PEIM modules in the same Firmware Volume. The maximum number of entries.
